{"about_the_game":"Omni Blade is an immersive and tactically challenging retro RPG inspired by classic games such as 7th Saga, Grandia, and Chrono Trigger. It features around 20 hours of gameplay, a thematically dense and dream-like narrative, as well as vibrantly colored pixel art - all brought to life by a beautifully evocative musical score! Omni Blade enhances replayability with procedurally generated levels and teammates that can be recruited in the order of your choosing. Built from the ground-up with a custom engine (Nu Game Engine), Omni Blade isn't your typical cookie-cutter indie RPG. If you're looking for the type of escapism and challenge from the old school era of console RPGs, Omni Blade promises you a captivating experience!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089800/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1724020291","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089800/page.bg.jpg?t=1724020291","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089800/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1724020291","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089800/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1724020291","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Omni Blade is an immersive and tactically challenging retro RPG inspired by classic games such as 7th Saga, Grandia, and Chrono Trigger. It features around 20 hours of gameplay, a thematically dense and dream-like narrative, as well as vibrantly colored pixel art - all brought to life by a beautifully evocative musical score! Omni Blade enhances replayability with procedurally generated levels and teammates that can be recruited in the order of your choosing. Built from the ground-up with a custom engine (Nu Game Engine), Omni Blade isn't your typical cookie-cutter indie RPG. I